            "value": "I've noticed when bcmath extension is enabled the problem with broken precision and number_format reoccurs.\r\n{code:title=Example from manual|borderStyle=solid}\r\n$number = Zend_Locale_Format::toNumber(13547.3678,\r\n                                       array('precision' => 2,\r\n                                             'locale' => $locale));\r\n{code}\r\nreturns 13547.36 with bcmath enabled. Zend Server 5.0, ZF 1.10.2, PHP 5.2.12, Windows 7.\r\nCorrect output should be 13547.37."
